data.name: DeleteDashboardOutputMetrics1
data.value: delete from CKT_DB_OUTPUT_MTRX where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId) and (TYPE = @type)
